title: Armin van Buuren - A State Of Trance 400 (2009-04-16) 123 tracks
description:
Hello Trance-Addicts!

Wow, what an amazing event! Impressive live sets by very talented DJs. It was so crowded, you could hardly breathe. The club was too small as it could cope that huge amount of clubbers!

The audio from di.fm is sometimes a little bit shitty but I didn't find any better source, so please be aware of those interruptions occuring sporadicly.

It was a hard job to tag all 123 files but hopefully I did a good job and all files are tagged properly. There are some IDs left but I gave my best to identify some of them.

And now put the entire event on your mp3-player and jump directly to your desired track of that massive celebration party!
